PN,30601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FThe US and Saudi Arabia have forged a
OL,8,Fnew agreement that could potentially
OL,9,Fprovide the kingdom with uranium
OL,10,Fenrichment capability for a civilian
OL,11,Fnuclear program.
OL,13,FUS Energy Secretary Chris Wright and
OL,14,FSaudi Minister of Energy Abdulaziz bin
OL,15,FSalman formally signed the nuclear
OL,16,Fcooperation agreement, known as a "123
OL,17,Fagreement," alongside what Donald
OL,18,FTrump's administration described as a
OL,19,F"bilateral safeguards agreement".
OL,26,@xD@cOUyD@KO]{D@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FThe US administration released few
OL,8,Fdetails of the deal, but the framework
OL,9,Fpaves the way for the building of a
OL,10,Furanium enrichment facility in Saudi
OL,11,FArabia after a joint US-Saudi study, a
OL,12,Fsource close to the deal told the
OL,13,FAssociated Press.
OL,15,F"These agreements reflect our two
OL,16,Fnations' shared commitment to
OL,17,Fstrengthening US-Saudi commercial
OL,18,Frelations, delivering prosperity at
OL,19,Fhome and security to our allies
OL,20,Fabroad," Wright said in a statement.
OL,26,@wD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,F"Rest assured, these agreements uphold
OL,8,Fthe highest standards of nuclear
OL,9,Fsafety and non-proliferation, while
OL,10,Frelying on the world's best nuclear
OL,11,Ftechnology and scientists, designed
OL,12,Fright here in the United States."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
