PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FEarlier, Secretary of State Marco
OL,8,FRubio sought to head off emerging
OL,9,Fcriticism of the decision under
OL,10,Fquestioning by reporters about the
OL,11,Frisk that helping the Saudis fulfil
OL,12,Ftheir long-standing desire to enrich
OL,13,Ftheir own uranium could lead to new
OL,14,Frounds of nuclear proliferation and
OL,15,Fcompetition in a volatile region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,F"The US is not going to reach any
OL,8,Fagreement with any country in the
OL,9,Fworld that leads to the risk of
OL,10,Fproliferation," said Rubio, who was
OL,11,Ftravelling in the Philippines on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FSome still have concerns that this
OL,15,Fdeal could open the door to
OL,16,Fweaponisation in the future, however.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
