FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FThe agreement does not include the
OL,8,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency's
OL,9,F(IAEA) Additional Protocol, which
OL,10,Fwould allow for more monitoring,
OL,11,Finspections and verification,
OL,12,Faccording to a second person familiar
OL,13,Fwith the decision.
OL,15,FThe deal is expected to last 30 years
OL,16,Fand involve US firms in developing the
OL,17,Fprogram. The Energy Department in a
OL,18,Fstatement said it will be submitted
OL,19,Ffor review to Congress, where it could
OL,20,Fface opposition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FSaudi Arabia's Energy Ministry said
OL,8,Fthe agreement bolsters "efforts to
OL,9,Fdiversify energy sources, advance
OL,10,Fcutting-edge technologies, and expand
OL,11,Fopportunities for cooperation and
OL,12,Finvestment in ways that serve the
OL,13,Fmutual interests of the two friendly
OL,14,Fcountries".
OL,16,FThe announcement comes as the US
OL,17,Fcontinues its war against Iran, a
OL,18,Fmajor regional rival of Saudi Arabia,
OL,19,Flaunched in part to prevent Tehran's
OL,20,Fability to develop a nuclear weapon.
OL,26,@pD@XOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FIran has insisted its nuclear
OL,8,Fenrichment program is peaceful,
OL,9,Falthough the IAEA has expressed
OL,10,Fconcerns over lack of transparency
OL,11,Ffrom the Islamic Republic.
OL,13,FConcerns over lack of oversight and
OL,14,Ffuture weaponisation
OL,16,FAhead of the announcement, Alexander
OL,17,FBollfrass, a nuclear expert at the
OL,18,FInternational Institute for Strategic
OL,19,FStudies in London, called the deal "a
OL,20,Frevolutionary new approach" to nuclear
OL,21,Fnon-proliferation policy.
OL,26,@{D@dOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,F"The revolutionary aspect of this
OL,8,Fagreement is that the United States is
OL,9,Fnot asking Saudi Arabia to abide by
OL,10,Fthe highest possible safeguards,
OL,11,Finternationally monitored safeguards
OL,12,Fthat are standard and are available
OL,13,Ftoday, but instead is willing to at
OL,14,Fleast theoretically transfer highly
OL,15,Fsensitive technology without the same
OL,16,Flevel of oversight that one would
OL,17,Fexpect," Bollfrass said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
