OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FPresident Trump, during his first
OL,8,Fterm, and former President Joe Biden
OL,9,Ftried to reach a nuclear deal with the
OL,10,Fkingdom to share American technology.
OL,12,FNon-proliferation experts warn any
OL,13,Fspinning centrifuges within Saudi
OL,14,FArabia could open the door to a
OL,15,Fpossible weapons program for the
OL,16,Fkingdom, something its assertive de
OL,17,Ffacto leader, Crown Prince Mohammed
OL,18,Fbin Salman, has suggested he could
OL,19,Fpursue if Tehran obtains an atomic
OL,20,Fbomb.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
