PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FWright travelled to Saudi Arabia last
OL,8,Fyear shortly before Trump visited and
OL,9,Fdiscussed building out the kingdom's
OL,10,Fcommercial nuclear power industry with
OL,11,Fhis Saudi counterpart.
OL,13,FAlready, Saudi Arabia and nuclear-
OL,14,Farmed Pakistan signed a mutual defence
OL,15,Fpact after Israel launched an attack
OL,16,Fon Qatar targeting Hamas officials.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
