PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784794688
OL,3,CUS and Saudi Arabia sign nuclear deal
OL,4,Cthat could allow kingdom to enrich
OL,5,Curanium
OL,7,FPakistan's defence minister then said
OL,8,Fhis nation's nuclear program "will be
OL,9,Fmade available" to Saudi Arabia if
OL,10,Fneeded, something seen as a warning
OL,11,Ffor Israel, long believed to be the
OL,12,FMiddle East's only nuclear-armed state.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
